            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName>Rolandus</persName> f. qd. <persName>Sismundi</persName> et
                            <persName>Atha</persName> iugalis fa. qd. *** et
                            <persName>Ermanno</persName> atque <persName>Stranbo</persName> germanii
                        filii eiusdem <persName>Rolandi</persName> et <persName>Guithone</persName>
                        qd. <persName>Massaioli</persName> et <persName>Guineldo</persName> f. eius
                        et <persName>Cacciato</persName> atque <persName>Moricone</persName> gg. qd.
                            <persName>Bernardi</persName>
                        <ref>ricevono da</ref>
                        <persName key="#Priors">Savinus</persName> prior <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesie</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3205">Sancti
                            Georgii</orgName> huius Lucane civitatis … <rs key="#Meritum/launechild"
                            >meritum</rs> anulum aurem; <ref>perciò promettono di</ref> litem nec
                        intentionem neque aliquam molestiam mittere neque facere … de una <rs
                            key="#Petiae">petia</rs> de terra que est in loco
                            <placeName>Cerbaria</placeName>, que est <rs key="#Forests">bossco et
                                <geogName ref="#estates/3201"
                                key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Wine #Hay/fodder"
                                >silva</geogName></rs> atque <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">prato</rs> atque <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra
                            culta et inculta</rs> atque agresta una cum omnibus edificiis que sunt
                        per circuitum ecclesie <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3204">Sancti
                            Nazari</orgName>, omnia insimul amembrata cuius fines ita sunt: ab uno
                        videlicet capite sicut crux est que vocatur Pisciatina, usque ad crucem
                        aliam sicut strada percurrit, et ex uno latere a suprascripta cruce
                        Pisciatina usque ad Valle de Fatuchaca et usque ad aquam de Palude, ex alio
                        latere sicut predicta crux alia esse videtur usque ad <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >rivum</rs> qui dicitur Ganbaraio et sicut ipse rivus percurrit usque ad
                        aqua de palude. <ref>Pena</ref>: pena argenti optimi libras viginti. Actum
                        intus <rs>castrum</rs> de <placeName>Via Venaria</placeName>.
                            <ref>(autografo)</ref> (S) <rs key="#Judge">Iudicis</rs> est signum
                            <persName key="#Judge">Ricardi</persName> pollice pictum. SM
                            <persName>Guililemi</persName> qd. <persName>Conceti</persName> et
                            <persName>Gallete</persName> qd. <persName>Gerardi</persName> et
                            <persName>Ciabactelli</persName> qd. <persName>Gualandi</persName> SM
                            <persName>Ildebrandi</persName> f. <persName>Bernardi</persName> et
                            <persName>Guiscardi</persName> f. <persName>Brunelli</persName>.
                            <ref>Scrive</ref>
                        <persName>Lanfrancus</persName> not domni regis. </ab>
